iction coefficient governing the quasi-static state in the creeping\nregime tends to a finite value for vanishing shear, which decreases the\ncritical friction coefficient by a factor of three for all cases investigated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Mar 2021 11:55:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Jun 2021 10:51:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
